Neighborhood: Golden Grove
Price: $750,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the picturesque neighborhood of Golden Grove. This spacious, move-in ready house features a stunning marble entryway, high ceilings, and ample natural light. The open-concept kitchen and living area boast granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a cozy fireplace, making it perfect for entertaining. The luxurious master suite features a walk-in closet and a spa-like bathroom with a jacuzzi tub. Enjoy stunning sunset views from the large backyard, complete with a covered patio and mature fruit trees.
Neighborhood Description: Located at the base of the Golden Mountain range, Golden Grove offers breathtaking views and a tranquil setting. With easy access to hiking trails and outdoor recreational activities, this neighborhood is perfect for nature enthusiasts. The community is also home to top-rated schools and is just a short drive from the bustling downtown area. Come experience the best of both worlds in Golden Grove.

Neighborhood: Golden Peak
Price: $1,200,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this luxurious mountain retreat in the prestigious neighborhood of Golden Peak. This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers premium finishes and stunning views of the surrounding peaks. The open-concept living and dining area feature high ceilings, exposed wood beams, and a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxing after a day on the slopes. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and ample counter space, ideal for hosting friends and family. Enjoy the tranquility and beauty of nature in this Golden Peak paradise.
Neighborhood Description: Golden Peak is the ultimate destination for outdoor enthusiasts and luxury living. Just a short drive to world-renowned ski resorts and hiking trails, this neighborhood offers year-round adventure. Take in the breathtaking mountain views while sipping on a locally-sourced latte from the Golden Peak Lodge. With a warm and friendly community, Golden Peak is the perfect balance of adventure and relaxation.

Neighborhood: Riverdale
Price: $650,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the charming neighborhood of Riverdale. The elegant brick exterior exudes sophistication and the expansive backyard is perfect for hosting summer BBQs. Inside, the hardwood floors and vaulted ceilings create a grand living space, perfect for entertaining guests. The recently renovated kitchen boasts modern appliances and granite countertops. Retreat to the luxurious master suite, complete with a walk-in closet and spa-like bathroom. Make this Riverdale gem your dream home.
Neighborhood Description:Escape the hustle and bustle of the city in the tranquil neighborhood of Riverdale. Surrounded by lush greenery, this community offers a peaceful and scenic environment. Enjoy a cup of coffee at the nearby Riverdale Cafe or take a leisurely stroll along the river. With easy access to local schools and parks, Riverdale is the perfect place for families. Don't miss out on the opportunity to join this idyllic neighborhood.

Neighborhood: Hidden Vale
Price: $1,200,000
Bedrooms: 5
Bathrooms: 4
House Size: 4,500 sqft
Description: Escape to this luxurious retreat in the enchanted neighborhood of Hidden Vale. This 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom estate offers the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. The stunning gourmet kitchen and grand living room are perfect for entertaining, while the large backyard with a sparkling pool and spa provides a perfect backdrop for relaxation. The elegant master suite offers a peaceful sanctuary with a spa-like bathroom and walk-in closets. Enjoy the serenity of Hidden Vale and its breathtaking views, just minutes away from bustling downtown.
Neighborhood Description: Hidden Vale is a magical community surrounded by lush forests and scenic trails. Get lost in the beauty of nature while living just minutes away from the bustling city life. Indulge in exquisite dining experiences at the nearby Enchanted Inn or take a leisurely bike ride through the charming streets, lined with beautiful homes and friendly neighbors. Come experience the enchanted lifestyle of Hidden Vale.

Neighborhood: Hidden Valley
Price: $950,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Escape to your own private retreat in the secluded and enchanting neighborhood of Hidden Valley. This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers unparalleled privacy and tranquility. The spacious living areas offer abundant natural light and lead to an expansive deck overlooking the lush surroundings. Upstairs, the master suite features a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a private balcony with a breathtaking view. Enjoy the serene and peaceful lifestyle of Hidden Valley in this one-of-a-kind home.
Neighborhood Description: Hidden Valley is a hidden gem, nestled in the hillside and surrounded by nature. Away from the hustle and bustle of the city, this neighborhood offers a peaceful escape with easy access to hiking trails and scenic viewpoints. Explore local art galleries, dine at cozy restaurants, or attend community events in the quaint town center. Experience the magic of Hidden Valley and discover your own personal sanctuary.

Neighborhood: Mystic Glen
Price: $1,200,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Step into this enchanting oasis located in the enchanting neighborhood of Mystic Glen. This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home showcases unique features such as a hand-carved front door and imported marble countertops. The spacious living area boasts high ceilings and plenty of natural light, perfect for entertaining. The dreamy backyard features a pool and spa, ideal for relaxation after a long day. Enjoy upscale living in the charming community of Mystic Glen.
Neighborhood Description: Mystic Glen is a magical escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. With quaint markets, charming cafes, and local artisans, this community is a blend of old-world charm and modern convenience. Take a stroll through the enchanting Glenwood Forest or attend the annual Renaissance Fair. With easy access to major highways, commuting is a breeze from this hidden gem of a neighborhood.

Neighborhood: Heavenly Haven
Price: $1,200,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Escape to your own personal sanctuary in the idyllic neighborhood of Heavenly Haven. This luxurious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers stunning views of the surrounding mountains and valley. The expansive living spaces are perfect for entertaining, featuring high ceilings, wood-burning fireplace, and oversized windows to take in the natural beauty outside. The chef's kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and ample counter space for culinary creations. Unwind in the master suite with its spa-like bathroom and private balcony. Experience tranquil living at its finest in Heavenly Haven.
Neighborhood Description: Heavenly Haven is a picturesque community known for its serene atmosphere and picturesque vistas. Enjoy hiking and biking trails through the nearby mountains, or take a short drive to the charming downtown area for shopping and dining. With top-rated schools and a strong sense of community, Heavenly Haven is the perfect place to call home.

Neighborhood: Rivendell
Price: $1,200,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,800 sqft
Description: Step into your own fairytale in this magical 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in the enchanting neighborhood of Rivendell. The charming exterior gives way to a spacious and elegant interior, with high ceilings and luxurious finishes. Cozy up by the fireplace in the grand living room, or bask in natural light in the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops and a center island. The first floor master suite boasts a luxurious spa-like bathroom and a walk-in closet fit for a king or queen. With a fenced backyard and a charming tree-lined street, this home is a dream come true.
Neighborhood Description: Rivendell is a quiet and idyllic community tucked away from the hustle and bustle of the city. Known for its stunning natural surroundings and sprawling estates, this neighborhood is a sanctuary for those seeking rest and relaxation. Enjoy a leisurely walk around the neighborhood's serene lake or take a short drive to Rivendell Village for trendy restaurants and boutique shopping. With picturesque views and easy access to hiking trails, Rivendell is perfect for those who love the great outdoors.

Neighborhood: Mystic Woods
Price: $650,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this enchanting home nestled in the whimsical Mystic Woods. This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom retreat offers a secluded yet modern living experience. The sprawling layout features a grand foyer with vaulted ceilings, perfect for hosting elegant dinner parties. The fully renovated kitchen boasts high-end appliances and a large island, ideal for cooking up gourmet meals. Cozy up by the fireplace in the sunken living room or take in the serene views from the private deck. Enjoy the magic of Mystic Woods in this stunning home.
Neighborhood Description: Mystic Woods is a charming neighborhood filled with picturesque homes and lush greenery. Residents can explore the nearby Secret Lake where they can spot mystical creatures and enjoy the tranquil surroundings. The community also offers a private park with walking trails and a playground for kids. With easy access to the highways and top-rated schools, Mystic Woods offers a perfect blend of seclusion and convenience. Embrace the magic of living in Mystic Woods.

Neighborhood:Silver City
Price:$1,200,000
Bedrooms: 5
Bathrooms: 4
House Size: 4,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this luxurious and spacious family home in the picturesque Silver City. This stunning 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home offers ample space for relaxation and entertainment with its open-concept living areas, including a chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances. A grand fireplace and floor-to-ceiling windows bring in natural light and warmth to the elegant living room. The expansive backyard with a sparkling pool and outdoor kitchen is perfect for summer gatherings. Retreat to the master suite with a spa-like bathroom and private balcony, while the kids have their own bedrooms and playroom. Experience the best of Silver City in this dreamy home.
Neighborhood Description: Silver City is a prestigious neighborhood renowned for its beautiful landscape, charming streets, and upscale amenities. Enjoy a morning jog in Maplewood Park or take the kids to the Silver City Farmers Market for fresh produce. This family-friendly neighborhood also offers top-rated schools, a variety of restaurants, and easy access to major highways for a quick commute. Experience the perfect blend of luxury and convenience in Silver City.

Neighborhood: Crystal Lake
Price: $675,000
Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 3
House Size: 2,500 sqft
Description: Welcome to this luxurious lakefront property in the exclusive community of Crystal Lake. This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers breathtaking views of the crystal-clear lake from every room. The open-concept layout features high ceilings, marble floors, and top-of-the-line appliances in the gourmet kitchen. Step outside to the expansive deck and private dock, perfect for entertaining or enjoying a day on the water. Indulge in a life of luxury and relaxation at this beautiful Crystal Lake retreat.
Neighborhood Description: Crystal Lake is an upscale, resort-style neighborhood with access to an abundance of outdoor activities and amenities. Spend your days boating, fishing, and swimming in the crystal-clear lake or take a leisurely bike ride around the scenic neighborhood. With fine dining options, boutique shops, and a vibrant nightlife, there is always something to do in Crystal Lake. Enjoy the best of both worlds at this serene lakeside community, just a short drive from the hustle and bustle of the city.
